description: As a user I should be able to search cars

children.name: Search the buy car with model
Search the buy car with model
And I mouse hover on "buy + sell" tab
Then I navigate to "New & Used Car Search" page
And I select location "NSW - Central Coast"
And I click on Find My Next Car tab
Then I should see the make "BMW" in results
